{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileSystem","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystem","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystem\"><code>FileSystem</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/root\"><code>root</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n <div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>在 <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\">File System API</a> 中，一个 <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileSystem\">FileSystem 对象</a>代表着一个文件系统。这个对象是调用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API#requestfilesystem\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">requestFileSystem() (en-US)</a> 成功的一个标志。FileSystem 对象有两个属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关于本文档","title":"关于本文档","isH3":false,"content":"<p>本文档的上次更新是 2012 年 3 月 2 日，引用来源是 2011 年 4 月 9 日的草案&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2011/WD-file-system-api-20110419/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Specifications (Working Draft)</a>。<br>\n <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/file-system-api/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">该草案</a>似乎已经被放弃了，任何实现不应该参考这份草案，也不该引用它。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本概念","title":"基本概念","isH3":false,"content":"<p>你可以通过调用 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API#requestfilesystem\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">window.requestFileSystem() (en-US)</a></code> 来请求对一个沙盒文件系统的访问权限。调用&nbsp;<code>requestFileSystem() </code>会创建一个新的沙盒存储空间。成功调用之后会返回一个 <code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileSystem\">FileSystem 对象</a></code>。它有两个属性：名称和文件系统的根目录。</p>\n\n<p><code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileSystem\">FileSystem 对象</a></code>是你访问文件系统所必须的，所以你最好为它创建一个引用，然后储存起来。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">属性</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">类型</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">解释</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a name=\"attr_name\"><code>name</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>只读的 DOMString</code></td>\n   <td>文件系统的名称。The name&nbsp;must&nbsp;be unique across the list of exposed file systems.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a name=\"attr_root\"><code>root</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>只读的目录实体</code></td>\n   <td>文件系统的根目录。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/entries-api/#api-domfilesystem","title":"File and Directory Entries API"}],"query":"api.FileSystem"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileSystem","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<p>引用：<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\">File System API</a></p>\n\n<p>介绍:&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_APIs/Filesystem/Basic_Concepts_About_the_Filesystem_API\">Basic Concepts About the File System API</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"关于本文档","id":"关于本文档"},{"text":"基本概念","id":"基本概念"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"在 File System API 中，一个 FileSystem 对象代表着一个文件系统。这个对象是调用 requestFileSystem() (en-US) 成功的一个标志。FileSystem 对象有两个属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/filesystem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/filesystem/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystem","title":"FileSystem"}],"pageTitle":"FileSystem - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}